title: Jellied Eels
content:
Jellied Eels are a category of item. It can be cooked in The Delectable Dab Kitchen in Hopeport using the Chef profession. Recipes for the Chef profession can be found in the Chef Recipe Book. Jellied Eels can be sold to Head Chef.


 * Lesser Jellied Eels
 * Gray Jellied Eels
 * Rocky Jellied Eels
 * Rord Jellied Eels
 * Moray Jellied Eels
 * Conger Jellied Eels
 * Leopard Jellied Eels
 * Greater Jellied Eels
